#. metadata.json->name
msgid "QRedshift"
msgstr "QRedshift"

#. metadata.json->description
msgid ""
"It makes the color of your computer's display adapt to the time of day, warm "
"at night and like sunlight during the day."
msgstr ""
"Stelt de kleur van uw beeldscherm af op het tijdstip van de dag: overdag "
"helder, 's avonds warm."

